Presenting Rumeli ~ The Summer Saga 

The JJ Valaya ~ Spring Summer 2022 Collection.

Given the depth and breadth of the Ottoman Empire, it’s no surprise that certain elements of its history continue to inspire the world. Back in the day, fashion was a manifestation of culture, people's lifestyles, and religious affiliation. Rumeli is an amalgamation of high fashion aesthetics and unparalleled luxury and promises to perfectly capture the soul of the season with an exquisite  assortment of colors, prints, embroideries and silhouettes. Prepare to immerse yourselves in a very special kind of visual splendor as we reveal our all new version of this season’s Rumeli .
